&lt;li&gt;Most importantly, you are a &lt;strong&gt;hustler in the best sense of the word&lt;/strong&gt;. You build relationships proactively, you spot opportunities before they&#39;re fully formed, and you thrive when you have ownership over growing a book of business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
